st two Staff of the Wheel pieces ...</span><hr size=1> Lake Rathe - Get invis and levitate and a 100+ swimming skill. Swim to the tower, grab the rod quickly and swom out asap. If a goblin aggros on you keep on swimming and press the /loc hotkey. If you die invis and go to thta loc and drag your corpse back up to serface.<br>
