<br>
Since getting the nice jump in power when I hit 29 this weekend, I've suddenly started having a lot more in the bank without even having to sell my services as a taxi. I'll stock up on both ITU and Enduring Breath potions. The shaman in my guild might be persuaded to let me buy at cost or near-cost.<br>
